        "message": "LU-16035 kfilnd: Use tn dispatch table\n\nChanging kfilnd_tn_event_handler() to use a dispatch table instead of\na switch statement results in another 1000-3000 RPC/s for LST 4K\nread/write operations.\n\nTest-Parameters: trivial\nHPE-bug-id: LUS-10119\nSigned-off-by: Ian Ziemba <ian.ziemba@hpe.com>\nChange-Id: I613bfd7bda985dfe8e08b3677e3bd7f23fa06d1f\n"
